verbose_text: In the present study, we determined the change in Snail, N-cadherin, and E-cadherin, the most representative EMT markers, in TSGA10 upregulated and down-regulated cells to show that TSGA10 might have a role in promoting bladder cancer cell metastasis by modulating the EMT pathway.
